headline.main: Sikh, Told to Leave Country, Shot in Washington State: Police
headline.print_headline: Sikh, Told to Leave Country, Shot in Washington State: Police

lead_paragraph: Chinese cities under pressure from soaring home prices need to boost land supply appropriately while authorities take targeted measures to fight an inventory overhang in smaller cities, Premier Li Keqiang said.
